name: TD Canadian Bank Dividend Index ETF
longDescription: TD Canadian Bank Dividend Index ETF seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses. This ETF invest in and hold a proportionate share or a sampling of constituent securities of the index to seek to track the performance of that index.
fulldescription: TD Canadian Bank Dividend Index ETF seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses. This ETF invest in and hold a proportionate share or a sampling of constituent securities of the index to seek to track the performance of that index. As an alternative to or in conjunction with investing in and holding the constituent securities, the ETF may also invest in other securities to obtain exposure to the constituent securities of the index in a manner that is consistent with the investment objectives of the ETF.
